00:46:42,000 --> 00:46:49,000
And so she'd go out and get him and bring him in because he wasn't driving by that time.

624
00:46:49,000 --> 00:46:53,000
So he just always came.

625
00:46:53,000 --> 00:46:56,000
That's a nice thing.

626
00:46:56,000 --> 00:46:57,000
That's good.

627
00:46:57,000 --> 00:47:00,000
So you had a woman who stayed in the house.

628
00:47:00,000 --> 00:47:02,000
And she had to feed him too.

629
00:47:02,000 --> 00:47:03,000
So care of things there.

630
00:47:03,000 --> 00:47:07,000
And then the rest of you packed off to Asia.

631
00:47:07,000 --> 00:47:08,000
Yes, we did.

632
00:47:08,000 --> 00:47:10,000
And then a very extravagant trip at that time.

633
00:47:10,000 --> 00:47:12,000
Oh, it was.

