1228
01:28:12,000 --> 01:28:17,000
You don't do this because your grandfather was this way.

1229
01:28:18,000 --> 01:28:28,000
And the other thing that I remember visibly, and I don't remember whether I told way this or not, but one day the teacher called me up when Kim was in school,

1230
01:28:28,000 --> 01:28:36,000
and she said, we're talking about letting the girls wear pants to school.

1231
01:28:36,000 --> 01:28:38,000
And what did I think about it?

1232
01:28:38,000 --> 01:28:40,000
And I said, it makes a lot of sense to me.

1233
01:28:40,000 --> 01:28:46,000
They turned their little bottoms upside down on all the playgrounds.

1234
01:28:46,000 --> 01:28:50,000
Well, you know, on the playground thing, I said, it makes a lot of sense to me.

1235
01:28:50,000 --> 01:28:59,000
And so that's when children, because otherwise I see pictures of my kids in their grade school era,

1236
01:28:59,000 --> 01:29:01,000
and they always had dresses on.

1237
01:29:01,000 --> 01:29:02,000
Sure.

